        <abstract>
            <p>Would like tabulation of horned beetles if not too troublesome, but would easily settle for general remarks.</p>
            <p>On the subject of other species mocking Heliconidae, asks whether full-coloured ones were mocked. Expresses full belief in HWB’s theory.</p> 
<p>Encloses a copy of A. R. Wallace’s letter to the <hi rend="italic">Field</hi> requesting observations on which caterpillars birds devour.</p> 
        </abstract>
